msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite_Entrance.item_boltcutter_on_fence.dlg.narrator"
msgid "There's no reason to do that."
msgstr "没有这样做的理由。"

msgid "(Why damage the fence when I can just cut the chain that locks the gate...?)"
msgstr "（我可以直接剪断锁住大门的铁链，为什么要破坏栅栏呢...？）"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite_Entrance.item_boltcutter_on_gate.dlg.narrator"
msgid "There's no reason to do that."
msgstr "没有这样做的理由。"

msgid "It's a little too late for that."
msgstr "现在做这个有点太迟了。"

msgid "I don't have all 3 keys yet..."
msgstr "我还没找到全部的3把钥匙..."

msgid "A gate locked with 3 padlocks."
msgstr "大门被3个挂锁锁住了。"

msgid "The warning sign reads:"
msgstr "警告牌上写着："

msgid "\"NO TRESPASSING. RISK OF SERIOUS INJURY OR DEATH\"."
msgstr "\"禁止入内。有严重伤亡风险\"。"

msgid "A fence blocks your path."
msgstr "围墙挡住了你的去路。"

msgid "I could've probably climbed over it... if not for those spikes."
msgstr "我也许能爬过去...如果没有那些刺的话。"

msgid "A lamppost."
msgstr "一盏路灯。"

msgid "I'm not confident in my ability to climb this and jump to the other side."
msgstr "我对自己爬上这里跳到另一边的能力没有信心。"

msgid "The note reads:"
msgstr "字条上写着："

msgid "\"Due to the recent primal incident, we ask residents stupid enough to go inside to close the gate behind you.\""
msgstr "“由于最近的原初恶魔事故，我们要求蠢到要进去的人关上背后的大门。”"

msgid "As expected, the back of the note is blank."
msgstr "跟预期的一样，字条的背面是空白的。"

msgid "A statue that looks out of place."
msgstr "一尊看起来格格不入的雕像。"

msgid "A torn piece of paper seems to be stuck underneath. Take it?"
msgstr "下面似乎粘着一张撕碎的纸。要拿出来吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite_Entrance.misc_statue.choice.A torn piece of paper seems to be stuck underneath. Take it?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite_Entrance.misc_statue.choice.A torn piece of paper seems to be stuck underneath. Take it?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "This path looks really dark and dangerous..."
msgstr "这条路看起来真的很黑，而且很危险..."

msgid "I went through the trouble of opening that gate but..."
msgstr "我费尽周折打开了那扇门，但是..."

msgid "I don't think there's a reason to go in there."
msgstr "我觉得没必要进去。"

msgid "I don't have any other sources of light..."
msgstr "我没有任何其他光源..."

msgid "Should I just use my phone's flashlight? It may be too bright..."
msgstr "我要直接用我手机的闪光灯吗？可能会太亮..."

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite_Entrance.move_enter.choice.Should I just use my phone's flashlight? It may be too bright..."
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite_Entrance.move_enter.choice.Should I just use my phone's flashlight? It may be too bright..."
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "I might not be able to come back after I go through here..."
msgstr "一旦我穿过这里，可能就回不来了..."

msgid "Continue down this path?"
msgstr "要继续沿着这条路走下去？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite_Entrance.move_enter.choice.Continue down this path?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite_Entrance.move_enter.choice.Continue down this path?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "I don't think I can help Kozmo by going this way..."
msgstr "我觉得走这条路帮不到科兹莫..."

msgid "Go in anyway?"
msgstr "无论如何也要进去吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite_Entrance.move_enter.choice.Go in anyway?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_Forest_LockedSite_Entrance.move_enter.choice.Go in anyway?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"
